$LANG:
bash -c 'case ${REPO_RREV} in
    ext_adp_s|ext_hero_s)
        git status
        git log -1
    ;;*) printf "\n${REPO_PATH}[%s]\n" "$1 $2"
esac;' - $USER $PWD

bash -c 'case ${REPO_RREV} in
    ext_adp_s|ext_hero_s)
        git status
        if [ "${REPO_PROJECT}" = "non_HLOS" ] || \
           [ "${REPO_PROJECT}" = "platform/Settings" ]; then
            echo ${HOME}
        else
            git log -1
        fi
    ;;*) printf "\n${REPO_PATH}[%s]\n" "$1 $2"
esac;' - $USER $PWD
